    <h1>Michigan Trucking &amp; Commercial Truck Insurance</h1>
    <p class="lead">Trucking carries some of the highest liability exposure on the road, and the wrong policy or a missed filing can park your business. We cover Michigan owner-operators and fleets with the liability, cargo, and physical-damage coverage carriers and shippers require.</p>

    <div class="trust-band">
